Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.58,0:03:05.86,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}深红之眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.98,0:03:09.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}即便道路布满荆棘我也绝不逃避
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.06,0:03:14.14,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}摹写一片结晶
